/NodeSepA ED /OffsetB ED /OffsetA ED tx@NodeDict a known tx@NodeDict b
known and dup { /NodeA a load def /NodeB b load def NodeA GetCenter /yA
ED /xA ED NodeB GetCenter /yB ED /xB ED } if } def
